vocabs
-------
sai - age
niju nana - 27
shusshin - home town
shigoto - work
shigoto no tame ni - for work / velaikaga 
sunde imasu - living
hataraku - velai
hataraite imasu - velai senju kondu eruthal (present continuos)
to-shite - as
san-nen han - 3 and half
keiken - experience
ichi-nen - 1 year
arimasu - erukiradhu
kazoku - family
nihon - Japan
hayaku - fast ah
nihongo - Japanese
benkyo - study/ padithal
benkyo shite - padithu vittu
hatarakitai - velai seiya virupam 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
watashino namae wa rajkumar desu (or) watashiwa rajkumar desu. niju nana sai desu.
my name is rajkumar (or) I am rajkumar. age is 27.

Shusshin wa coimbatore desu. watashi wa shigoto no tame ni chennai ni sunde imasu.
Home-town is coimbatore. I live in chennai for my work.

Ima HCL de hataraite imasu. Sofutou enginiya to-shite san-nen han no keiken to Quality enginiya to-shite ichi-nen no keiken ga arimasu
Now working in HCL.I have 3 and half years of experience as software engineer and 1 year of experience as Quality engineer.

(Please explain your technical skills in English only, No problem)

kazoku wa san nin desu. chichi to haha to imoto desu. 
family la 3 per. appa,amma,thangchii.

imoto wa nihon de hataraite imasu, kanagawa ni sunde imasu.
thangchi working in japan.she live in kanagawa

watashimo  hayaku nihongo o benkyo-shite, nihon de hatarakitai n desu.
nanum sekrama japanese ai padichu,japan la velia seiyanumnu asai padren

ijou desu. yoroshiku onegai shimasu. arigatou gozaimasu.
(shimasu vida itashimasu - more polite, ungaluku kastama eruntha shimasu matum potukonga)
Thats all, Thank you
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
watashino namae wa rajkumar desu (or) watashiwa rajkumar desu. niju nana sai desu.
Shusshin wa coimbatore desu. watashi wa shigoto no tame ni chennai ni sunde imasu.
Ima HCL de hataraite imasu. Sofutou enginiya to-shite san-nen han no keiken to Quality enginiya to-shite ichi-nen no keiken ga arimasu
kazoku wa san nin desu. chichi to haha to imoto desu. 
imoto wa nihon de hataraite imasu, kanagawa ni sunde imasu.
watashimo  hayaku nihongo o benkyo-shite, nihon de hatarakitai n desu.
ijou desu. yoroshiku onegai shimasu. arigatou gozaimasu.



